{"tid":1972540,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴.而我不知道索拿斯是誰","createTime":"2020-04-14T14:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T10:55:28.000Z","uid":193217,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c546109e052453a3f68f0599104098277a1da5d3","tid":1972540,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:49:03.000Z","msg":"現參與球評工作的桑拿士曾批評普巴實力，還有對方並沒認真對待傷患復康治療。普巴回應：「我連桑拿士是誰也不知道，我聽說他曾是頂級球員，聽過他的名字，但我不認得他的樣子。我不是一個常留意評論的人，我看很多球賽，但很少在賽後留下來聽他們評述。我喜歡專注於足球。」<br />\n<br />\n說到批評這件事，普巴補充：「他們想念我，是吧？當我重看比賽，我留意的不是評論。當你認識足球，你不需別人告訴你發生甚麼事。當我聽到別人說普巴怎樣怎樣，不知道呢，或者有天我會碰上他們，然後直接提問，因為我真的想知為甚麼。」這位法國球星亦強調自己有做復康治療。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=17b4b369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你咩.唔比人唔識你嫁.依家加歷查又加入戰團<br />\n話你點可能唔識索拿斯..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曼聯球員點解要識你利狗班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a59e0e0217b79fd2801f7d66611664673fa59d1","tid":1972540,"uid":193217,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"桑拿士先好笑<br />\n叫大家show獎牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普巴.下一步可能串柒佢.你有冇世界杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08b5329e5b0560c9a7c79ba0cc4cac907519234","tid":1972540,"uid":349872,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"拿索斯我就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e424103eebaad400d32a5da39c36b804285fed","tid":1972540,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"利記班人真係好撚好笑<br />\n唔比唔識你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30bb580c0902a723ca56792ff4ac1f57d72c324","tid":1972540,"uid":15236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T15:20:00.000Z","msg":"索拿斯仲好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77c5ea6cf453392a983089c5b89318d85f3c17a","tid":1972540,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"索拿斯咪就係買英超第一水貨嗰條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bc84b4b7681bd419e6a93f89d960e83a3356ee","tid":1972540,"uid":203961,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c08b5329e5b0560c9a7c79ba0cc4cac907519234","tid":1972540,"uid":349872,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"拿索斯我就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"香討拿鐵斯我就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5395a03d6ff558beb3a60de9cbaa48a5e2dbb40e","tid":1972540,"uid":33730,"like":0